The paper also introduces a new graph representation for encoding operations, which could fall under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI). The use of classic multi-terminal networks such as the multi-access channel, broadcast channel, and interference channel suggests a focus on communication and computation (cs.CC). Finally, the use of statistical properties and typical sets suggests a focus on data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
